description:
This course will help you assess you current use of time then teach you some easy to use tools and techniques that will help you to manage yourself effectively around the available time in the day.

As an entrepreneurs we often operate on a different time pattern to the average working person, so we need to be more careful and manage our time better in order to achieve all the functions and tasks that we are required to complete each day, week and month.
title: Time Management for Entrepreneurs
